  "script": "There's a lizard that can do something that looks impossible, it runs straight across the surface of water. It's the basilisk, nicknamed the Jesus Christ lizard. When a predator strikes, it drops onto a pond and sprints across the top on its back legs, slapping the water so fast that air pockets form under its feet and keep it from sinking. A small one can cross fifteen feet before it starts to swim. It's pure panic engineered into a superpower. So what happens the moment it finally runs out of speed?",
